{"type": "article", "id": 25597, "title": "实验风格灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-18T07:08:41Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607185024CUK63IY7JdHMSsyr.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一盏有实验风格的灯，来自印度刚毕业不久的设计师 Rashmeet Saggu。其中一盏灯就像是利用实验时常用的圆锥瓶改造的，瓶口接上了灯，瓶子作为玻璃灯泡使用，留在瓶子上的白色刻度提醒了它从前的用途，有旧物利用的质朴和原始。另一种灯保留了圆锥形的形状，更明亮。连接灯泡的线绕了一个圈，可以直接挂在墙上。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185022LhJ0DoSbrIYksVud.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.70666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185022KSyB2iVZj1OUg769.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185023wFfsPD8EU0QXGS1R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071850239d2SJpLlrcFHaB8Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65904762\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}